<seg id="14">The amount that beneficiaries will lose depends on the size of the family.</seg>
<seg id="15">For a family of four receiving the maximum amount, monthly benefits will fall to $632 from $668, or a decline of $36, according to the Agriculture Department.</seg>
<seg id="16">The maximum benefits for a single adult would fall to $189 from $200, or by $11.</seg>
