<seg id="1">Living together in French is the challenge facing the Commission Scolaire Marguerite-Bourgeoys (Marguerite Bourgeoys School Board).</seg>
<seg id="2">At the Marguerite-Bourgeoys School Board, 62% of students have a mother tongue other than French.</seg>
