<seg id="1">Toronto Mayor Chases Off Journalists Seeking to Interview Him on Drug Affair</seg>
<seg id="2">In Canada, the Mayor of Toronto is suspected of using drugs, according to several media sources.</seg>
<seg id="3">A video sent to the authorities seems to support these suspicions.</seg>
<seg id="4">The man concerned, Rob Ford, has always denied having taken crack, but has admitted being partial to cannabis.</seg>
<seg id="5">This Thursday he drove a number of journalists off his property when they came to interview him.</seg>
