<seg id="1">Beijing Blames Turkoman Islamic Movement</seg>
<seg id="2">"Behind-the-scenes support for the attack came from the East Turkestan Islamic Movement (ETIM) based in central and western Asia," declared the head of the Chinese security services to a Hong Kong television channel, according to a video posted online on Thursday evening.</seg>
