<seg id="7">"He thought, when it came to this particular policy, I had no sense of the reality of the business world," he said.</seg>
<seg id="8">Ex-ALP heavyweight Joe Tripodi has been drawn into ICAC inquiry dealing with Eddie Obeid's Circular key businesses.</seg>
<seg id="9">Mr Obeid is being investigation by the Independent Commission against Corruption over claims he misused his position as an MP to lobby four consecutive ports ministers about the Circular Quay retail leases, where his family had a secret interest.</seg>
