<seg id="273">Like Les Dawson, he's pretending to be crap.</seg>
<seg id="274">Which you can only do if you're a genius.</seg>
<seg id="275">Anyway, no one else noticed Samuel Beckett there and I had a job persuading them afterwards that I had actually seen him.</seg>
