<seg id="1">Vatican Poll on Contraception, Divorce and Homosexuality</seg>
<seg id="2">The Vatican is to carry out a large-scale poll across the world on the way in which parishes handle sensitive issues such as contraception, divorces and same-sex couples.</seg>
