<seg id="4">The poll was sent out to every national conference of bishops in mid-October, with instructions to secure as many responses as possible.</seg>
<seg id="5">The information will be used at a major assembly on the family that Pope Francis is planning to organize next year.</seg>
<seg id="6">The news was reported on Thursday by the National Catholic Reporter, an independent Catholic newspaper in the United States.</seg>
