<seg id="1">World Squash 2013: Nick Matthew ousts Egypt's Amr Shabana to set up thrilling semi-final with Ramy Ashour</seg>
<seg id="2">The Yorkshireman mustered an array of tight, angled winners, the Egyptian racking up an uncharacteristic number of tins.</seg>
<seg id="3">Matthew didn't over-complicate matters and, again, he put this down to his off-court work.</seg>
