<seg id="6">They don't clutter your mind, they are simple thoughts and you need those against Ramy [Ashour], who can beat you very quickly.</seg>
<seg id="7">Ashour largely did that to India's Saurav Ghosal, but the surprise quarter-finalist made him work in the first and third games.</seg>
