<seg id="2">Air France-KLM has written off the value of its 25 percent stake in Italy's financially-troubled Alitalia.</seg>
<seg id="3">In its latest results, the Franco-Dutch firm said it was taking a charge of 119 million euros against profits to cover that.</seg>
