<seg id="2">Archetype Studio Inc.</seg>
<seg id="3">Now that Kelly Clarkson has married into a country family, it should come as no surprise that she prefers country stars to her pop peers.</seg>
<seg id="4">"It is funny, I do relate way more to country stars," Clarkson told the latest issue of TIME.</seg>
